---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Lightbox from '../../components/Lightbox.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';
import mindmapData from '../../data/mindmap-en.json';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Giora, 72 years old, 42 selling trips, and an AI that won't let me sleep." lang="en" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header lang="en" />
		<main>
			<h1>About me</h1>
			<p><strong>I'm Giora.</strong> I'm 72 and I've spent 42 years selling trips. The other 30 I spent cycling, skiing, diving, working, partying and trying to chat people up. Not necessarily in that order.</p>
			<p>I run Viajes Scibasku from Marbella -- ski, diving, experiences you won't find on Google. CICMA 2283. One agency, one man, and now an artificial intelligence that won't let me sleep.</p>
			<p>Because suddenly everything changed.</p>
			<p>Diabetes took away my nightly gin & tonics. I swapped them for YouTube. YouTube led me to artificial intelligence. And artificial intelligence rejuvenated my mind by 30 years. Now I automate what used to take a whole team, generate premium quotes in minutes, have a Mac Mini that works while I sleep, and still don't understand half of what I do -- but it works.</p>
			<p>This blog tells that story. The discoveries, the disasters, the 3AM nights wrestling with technology that didn't exist when I started travelling. If you're over 50 and think AI isn't for you, stick around. If you're 25 and think you know it all, same.</p>

			<h2>How this blog works</h2>
			<p>Things don't go in order here. One day I tell you about something I discovered yesterday. The next I take you to an August night in 2025 when I wrote my first prompt without knowing what a prompt was. And the day after that I talk about what I think is coming next.</p>
			<p>Past, present and future -- mixed like a good terrace conversation. Because that's how my head works since AI rewired it: everything connected, everything at once, everything at 3 in the morning.</p>

			<hr />

			<!-- Infographic portrait -->
			<section class="infografia-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">My rewiring in images</h2>
				<div class="infografia-container">
					<img
						src="/images/recableado-portrait.webp"
						alt="Rewired at 72: AI - full infographic of the transformation"
						class="infografia-img zoomable"
						loading="lazy"
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="infografia-actions">
					<a href="/images/recableado-portrait.webp" download="recableado-infografia.webp" class="btn-secondary">
						Download infographic
					</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<hr />

			<!-- Interactive mind map -->
			<section class="mindmap-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">My mind map</h2>
				<div class="mindmap-container">
					<div class="mindmap-root">
						<span class="mindmap-root-label">{mindmapData.name}</span>
					</div>
					<div class="mindmap-branches">
						{mindmapData.children.map((branch: any) => (
							<details class="mindmap-branch">
								<summary class="branch-title">{branch.name}</summary>
								<ul class="branch-items">
									{branch.children?.map((child: any) => (
										<li class="branch-item">
											{child.children ? (
												<details class="mindmap-subbranch">
													<summary class="subbranch-title">{child.name}</summary>
													<ul class="subbranch-items">
														{child.children.map((sub: any) => (
															<li class="subbranch-item">{sub.name}</li>
														))}
													</ul>
												</details>
											) : (
												<span>{child.name}</span>
											)}
										</li>
									))}
								</ul>
							</details>
						))}
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="mindmap-caption">Mind map generated by NotebookLM from 18 sources</p>
			</section>

			<hr />

			<!-- NotebookLM Videos -->
			<section class="media-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">The full picture</h2>
				<p class="media-intro">3 videos generated by NotebookLM from 18 sources about my rewiring.</p>

				<div class="video-grid">
					<div class="video-card">
						<video controls preload="metadata" playsinline>
							<source src="https://res.cloudinary.com/drqgkirpy/video/upload/v1770579619/recableado/el-viaje-de-giora.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
						</video>
						<h3 class="video-title">Giora's Journey</h3>
						<p class="video-desc">The full story: from gin & tonics to AI</p>
					</div>

					<div class="video-card">
						<video controls preload="metadata" playsinline>
							<source src="https://res.cloudinary.com/drqgkirpy/video/upload/v1770579624/recableado/el-viajero-recableado.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
						</video>
						<h3 class="video-title">The Rewired Traveller</h3>
						<p class="video-desc">A travel agent who reinvented himself at 72</p>
					</div>

					<div class="video-card">
						<video controls preload="metadata" playsinline>
							<source src="https://res.cloudinary.com/drqgkirpy/video/upload/v1770579629/recableado/recableado-mental-ia-72.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
						</video>
						<h3 class="video-title">Mental rewiring with AI at 72</h3>
						<p class="video-desc">How artificial intelligence rejuvenated my mind</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<hr />

			<!-- Contact -->
			<section class="contact-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
				<div class="contact-card">
					<p class="contact-text">If you want to talk about AI, travel, or why diabetes was the best thing that happened to me, write to me. If you want me to give a talk at your company or event about how a 72-year-old man automated his business without knowing how to code, also.</p>
					<a href="mailto:giora@viajesscibasku.com" class="contact-email">
						giora@viajesscibasku.com
					</a>
					<p class="contact-talks">I also give talks -- more info coming soon</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer lang="en" />
		<Lightbox />
	</body>
</html>
<style>
	/* Infographic */
	.infografia-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin: 2em 0;
	}
	.infografia-container {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}
	.infografia-img {
		max-width: 500px;
		width: 100%;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26, 54, 93, 0.15);
	}
	.infografia-actions {
		margin-top: 1.2em;
	}

	/* Mind map */
	.mindmap-section {
		margin: 2em 0;
	}
	.mindmap-container {
		background: var(--heading);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 2em;
		color: white;
	}
	.mindmap-root {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}
	.mindmap-root-label {
		font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.3em;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--naranja);
	}
	.mindmap-branches {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.6em;
	}
	.mindmap-branch {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		border-radius: 8px;
		border-left: 3px solid var(--naranja);
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.branch-title {
		font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 1em;
		padding: 0.8em 1em;
		cursor: pointer;
		list-style: none;
		color: white;
	}
	.branch-title::-webkit-details-marker {
		display: none;
	}
	.branch-title::before {
		content: '\25B8 ';
		color: var(--naranja);
		transition: transform 0.2s;
	}
	.mindmap-branch[open] > .branch-title::before {
		content: '\25BE ';
	}
	.branch-items {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0 1em 0.8em 2em;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.branch-item {
		padding: 0.3em 0;
		font-size: 0.9em;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
		line-height: 1.5;
	}
	.mindmap-subbranch {
		margin: 0.2em 0;
	}
	.subbranch-title {
		cursor: pointer;
		font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
		list-style: none;
		font-size: 0.95em;
	}
	.subbranch-title::-webkit-details-marker {
		display: none;
	}
	.subbranch-title::before {
		content: '\25B8 ';
		color: var(--naranja);
		font-size: 0.8em;
	}
	.mindmap-subbranch[open] > .subbranch-title::before {
		content: '\25BE ';
	}
	.subbranch-items {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0.2em 0 0 1.2em;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.subbranch-item {
		padding: 0.15em 0;
		font-size: 0.88em;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
	}
	.mindmap-caption {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 0.85em;
		color: var(--gray);
		margin-top: 0.8em;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	/* Videos */
	.media-section {
		margin: 2em 0;
	}
	.media-intro {
		color: var(--gray);
		font-size: 0.95em;
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}
	.video-grid {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5em;
	}
	.video-card {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: box-shadow 0.2s ease;
	}
	.video-card:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(26, 54, 93, 0.1);
	}
	.video-card video {
		width: 100%;
		display: block;
		background: #000;
		border-radius: 0;
	}
	.video-title {
		font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.05em;
		color: var(--heading);
		margin: 0.8em 1em 0.2em;
		font-weight: 600;
	}
	.video-desc {
		font-size: 0.88em;
		color: var(--gray);
		margin: 0 1em 0.8em;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	/* Contact card */
	.contact-section {
		margin: 2em 0;
	}
	.contact-card {
		background: #fef5e7;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--naranja);
		padding: 1.5em 2em;
	}
	.contact-text {
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}
	.contact-email {
		display: inline-block;
		font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.1em;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--heading);
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
	.contact-email:hover {
		color: var(--naranja);
	}
	.contact-talks {
		font-size: 0.9em;
		color: var(--gray);
		margin: 0;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.mindmap-container {
			padding: 1.2em;
		}
		.mindmap-root-label {
			font-size: 1.1em;
		}
		.contact-card {
			padding: 1.2em;
		}
	}
</style>
